title: "When beauteous Myra...lifts her eyes..."
description: Folio. Interior. At right figure of woman is seated, looking toward head of a man, seen in a halo of light. Figure of Cupid points the way. Table at left, with globe and open book. Eight lines of verse below. Decorative border.
name: Greeting card
